    "text": "The Fisheries and Resources Monitoring System (FIRMS) of the United Nations Food and Agriculture Organization (FAO) provides global monthly catches from tuna fisheries by 5° grid from 1950 to 2024 (FIRMS level 0).",
    "topic": "FIRMS tuna fisheries data"
  },
  {
    "text": "The repository associated with FIRMS includes code and data used for the study titled 'One to Three-Day Lead Streamflow Forecast Using Multi-Head Attention with Long Short-Term Memory in Reservoir Regulated Catchment'.",
    "topic": "FIRMS repository content"
  },
  {
    "text": "The dataset compiled by FIRMS is intended for use in global annual catch assessments at FIRMS level 0.",
    "topic": "FIRMS dataset purpose"
  },
  {
    "text": "The FIRMS dataset compiles nominal catches from global tuna fisheries across five tuna Regional Fisheries Management Organizations (t-RFMOs).",
    "topic": "FIRMS dataset scope"
  },
  {
    "text": "A systematic data flow process has been developed under the auspices of the Fisheries and Resources Monitoring System (FIRMS) of the FAO.",
    "topic": "FIRMS data flow process"
  }
